room_title: Escape room "The Cure" by Avalanche Escape Rooms in Anchorage
room_description: His only daughter poisoned, Dr. Roca has been blackmailed to create a deadly nerve agent. Racing against the clock, he risked it all to find a cure for his daughter. But now he’s missing, and she’s not long for this world. Join Dr. Roca’s most trusted friend and colleague to break into the underground lab where nothing is quite as it seems, find the cure, and escape before you too fall victim to this sinister plot.
